Author: obviouslynotjackie
Text: Girl, I’m an expert at this stuff. I have orange peels and banana peels, Dole fruit cups and apple cores and spinach in my trash can right now and idc.   Meat (I only eat chicken) will probably last a week before it starts getting moldy. It starts getting smelly on day 2-3, especially if it’s hot in the room. It’ll be fine :)
